  "lifecycle_summary": "run() bootstraps telemetry, opens Postgres and the graph backend, calls buildReducerService to wire all domain handlers and runners, mounts the shared admin surface via app.NewHostedWithStatusServer, then calls service.Run under a SIGINT/SIGTERM signal context. Shutdown is triggered by os.Interrupt or syscall.SIGTERM; the hosted runtime drains in-flight work before returning.",
